  <brief_title>Chidamide Plus R-CHOP in Elderly DLBCL</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Single Arm, Open-label, Phase II Study of Chidamide in Combination With R-CHOP in the Treatment of de Novo, Elderly, High-risk Diffuse Large B-cell Lymphoma</official_title>
