  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a prospective, single-arm, open-label phase II study of Chidamide in combination with
      R-CHOP in the treatment of de novo, elderly, high-risk diffuse large B cell lymphoma
      patients.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
